Yawan adadin cutar korona (COVID-19) da ke ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Yawan kamuwa da cutar korona (COVID-19) yana nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya, wanda ya tabbatar da cewa ko da yake matakin ya bambanta daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, cutar COVID-19 tana daɗa muni a cikin dukkan ƙasashe.
Bisa ga abin da Italiya ta samu, ya kamata ƙasashe da asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya su kara kasancewa a shirye don ƙara yawan marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 da za su bukaci kula da lafiya, musamman kula da marasa lafiya.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an bayar da rahoton wasu cututtukan cututtukan huhu na rashin sananne a birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, a kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Sukan Ciwo da Rigakafin Cutar Sin ta ruwaito cewa abin da ke haddasa shi ne sabon kwayar cutar Corona, wanda yanzu ake kira kwayar cutar Corona 2 da ke da alaƙa da cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga lokacin, an kira cutar da ta haifar da SARS-CoV-2 cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Dalilin ya zuwa yanzu shi ne cewa kusan kashi 80 cikin dari na mutanen da ke da cutar COVID-19 suna da wata cuta mai sauƙi; wato, suna da kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi tare da alamun bayyanar cututtuka ko a'a, kuma yawancin suna warkewa.
A kusan kashi 14 cikin ɗari, kamuwa da COVID-19 ya zama mafi tsanani da ke bukatar yin asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin ɗari na sauran marasa lafiya suna fama da mummunan cuta da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka yi asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin yawan adadin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Burtaniya (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da na lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya da na Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
An samu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya
Bayan abin da ya faru a China, COVID-19 ya bazu a wurare dabam-dabam kuma halin da ake ciki na COVID-19 a sauran ƙasashen duniya yana bin halin da ake ciki na wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na WHO ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin Eurosurveillance na 5 ga Maris, 2020, Spiteri da sauransu sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbacin COVID-19 na Turai bisa ga bayanin WHO na halin da ake ciki.
A cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon shari'o'i uku na tabbatarwa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 ga mutanen da ke dawowa daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai 30 da Burtaniya (UK), inda tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 zuwa wannan kwanan wata, an ruwaito shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin da kuma adadin adadin COVID-19
A Cibiyar Tarayyar Turai don Yin Rigakafi da Rigakafin Cututtuka (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a duniya, ana samun su ne kawai daga tushen hukuma kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya a ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, a kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimantawa da kwatanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya da na Italiya.
A matsayin ma'auni na yaduwar COVID-19, mun lissafa jimlar adadin COVID-19 na yau da kullum a cikin kwanaki 14, sannan mu yi la'akari da yanayin COVID-19, a duk ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya, a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma ba da jimlar adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito daga kowace ƙasa daga 15 ga Maris, 2020 da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe, tare da kwatanta shi da adadin da aka samu a Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Hanyoyin COVID-19 a cikin EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya
An bi kwatancen adadin adadin COVID-19 da aka samu a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya na lardin Hubei (China) (Figure 1).
Ga EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya gabaɗaya, jimlar COVID-19 ta fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ta ƙaru sosai a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (ƙarin bayani).
Wannan ya kasance ne saboda yawan adadin da aka samu daga Italiya, amma duk ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwar adadin COVID-19 (abin da ya dace).
Hoton 2 ya nuna jimlar adadin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Birtaniya sun ba da rahoton jimlar adadin shari'o'in da suka yi kama da na Italiya makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da aka samu na COVID-19 suna ƙaruwa sosai a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Birtaniya.
Hanyoyin da aka lura a cikin adadi na COVID-19 sun nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, duk da bambancin amsoshin lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, kuma akwai yiwuwar bambancin yanayin a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban da ladabi don zaɓar marasa lafiya da za a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin bi.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kusan kashi 10 cikin dari na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 ke bukatar kulawa ta musamman. Majiyoyin watsa labarai sun ruwaito cewa asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai ga iyakar ƙarfin su.
A halin yanzu akwai bayanai game da shigar asibitoci da/ko cibiyoyin kula da mutane da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 a EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai na kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'in a jere (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara su a hanyar da za ta iya kammala bayanan kulawar da ake yi a yanzu, wanda ya dogara da yawan adadin da aka samu da kuma yawan mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 2010-11 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin yawan iyalan da ke kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, wato, iyalan da ke kula da marasa lafiya a Jamus sun kai 29.2 a ƙasar Jamus, kuma iyalan da ke kula da marasa lafiya a ƙasar Portugal sun kai 4.2 a kowace mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 gadaje na kulawa mai tsanani da matsakaici ga kowane mutum 100,000 a 201011).
Ana samun samfurin yanayin da ke da alaƙa da gamsar da iyawar kula da lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa daga cikin ƙasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya don yaduwar COVID-19 da aka shigar da asibiti da ke da haɗari &gt; 90% don wuce ƙarfin gidajen kulawa na musamman, a cikin sabuntawa ta shida don kimanta haɗarin COVID-19 na gaggawa na Cibiyar Turai don Yaki da Cututtuka da Rigakafi.
Tun da yake asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya da ke cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya sun kasance a wasu yankuna, yawanci asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya suna aiki a wasu yankuna, ana so a ba da bayani game da asibitoci da kuma iyali na cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya a matsayin Sunan Cibiyoyin Kula da Yanki na 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana daɗa muni a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, ya kamata kasashe da asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya su shirya kansu don yanayin canjin zamantakewar al'umma na SARS-CoV-2 da kuma karuwar yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke bukatar kula da lafiya, musamman ma cibiyar kula da marasa lafiya, kamar yadda yake faruwa a yankunan da aka shafa a Italiya.
A cewar cibiyar Turai ta yaki da cututtuka da kuma hana su, an nuna cewa tsarin gaggawa na gaba ɗaya na gaggawa yana da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 yayin da aka sauya tsarin hanawa zuwa ragewa, saboda ƙaruwa mai sauri a cikin adadin lokuta na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci lokaci mai yawa don fahimta, karɓa da daidaita amsar su idan ba a aiwatar da su ba.
Ana kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai iyakacin damar da kasashe za su iya ƙara yin tsaro don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma rage matsa lamba a kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan hakan bai yi nasara ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya a cikin ƙasashen EU/kasashen tattalin arzikin Turai na iya fuskantar karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa ta musamman a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar korona ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda cutar korona ta 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ke haifarwa, ta kashe mutane fiye da 3,000 kuma ta jikkata mutane fiye da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'in bil'adama.
SARS-CoV-2 kamar SARS-CoV, wanda ya sa dubban mutane suka kamu da cutar SARS a shekara ta 2003, zai iya zama sanadiyyar cutar daga bats kuma ya haifar da irin wannan bayyanar ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙananan haɗari da mutuwar fiye da SARS amma yana da tasiri da tasiri tsakanin tsofaffi fiye da matasa da tsakanin maza fiye da mata.
A sakamakon yawan wallafe-wallafen da ake yi game da cututtukan da ke tasowa, wannan talifin yana neman ya ba da cikakken bayani game da batun bincike da ke ci gaba da sauri.
Za mu tattauna abubuwan da suka shafi annobar cutar, abubuwan da ke haddasa ta, ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaya da kuma rigakafinta.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da za a amsa, muna fata wannan bita zai taimaka mana mu fahimci cutar da ke barazana kuma mu kawar da ita.
Bikin bazara na 25 ga Janairu 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba a taɓa mantawa da shi ba ga dukan 'yan kasar Sin da aka bukaci su zauna a gidajensu a lokacin hutu da kuma makonni da yawa bayan haka saboda sabon annobar cutar.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana kama da cutar Corona (Cov) wadda ta haifar da barkewar cutar ta SARS a shekara ta 2003. Saboda haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta kira ta SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma an kira cutar da ke da alaƙa da cutar Cov-19 (Covid-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma nan da nan ta bazu ko'ina cikin kasar, da kuma kusan wasu kasashe 50 a duniya.
Ya zuwa 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da kamuwa da COVID-19 guda 80,000, tare da fitar da marasa lafiya sama da 40,000 daga asibitoci da mutuwar marasa lafiya sama da 3,000.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 ita ce magabcin jama'a na 1 kuma yana iya zama mafi ƙarfi fiye da ta'addanci.
A cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga bincike sama da 200 game da COVID-19 wanda ya haɗa da ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, annoba, abubuwan da ke haifar da shi, ganewar asali, da magani, tun lokacin da aka fitar da rahoto na farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 wanda ya gano jerin ƙwayoyin cuta na marasa lafiya da yawa.
Wannan bita na nufin taƙaita ci gaban bincike a sabon batun da ke ci gaba da sauri.
A duk inda za mu iya, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wani cuta da Coff ya yi, wato cutar ta numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS), wanda ya barke a shekara ta 2012.
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya game da rigakafin cututtuka da kuma yin hasashen cutar da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci da za a yi.
Ana ganin cewa kwayar cutar korona ce ke haddasa cututtuka marasa mutuwa a cikin mutane, kuma a zahiri tana haddasa kusan kashi 15 cikin 100 na cututtukan sanyi na kowa.
Duk da haka, a wannan karni, mun fuskanci cututtukan coronavirus sau biyu masu haddasa cututtukan mutum, SARS-CoV da MS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da barkewar cutar a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, bi da bi, kuma cutar ta bazu cikin wasu ƙasashe da sauri tare da yawan yaduwar cutar da mutuwar.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine annoba ta uku ta coronavirus a tarihin ɗan adam.
