Ka lura cewa ko da yake COVID-19 sabuwar cuta ce, hankali da sani namu suna ƙaruwa bisa sakamakon bincike da kuma gwajin asibiti; saboda haka ana sabunta hanyoyin bincike da magani a kai a kai.
Alal misali, a tsakanin 16 ga Janairu 2020 da 3 ga Maris 2020, an fitar da jagororin bincike da maganin COVID-19 na Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta Jamhuriyar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn), jimlar fitowa bakwai tare da wasu mahallin da aka canza.
Yanzu, shawarwarinmu na jagora sun amsa da wani bayani daga Chu da wasu, waɗanda suka gabatar da wata shawara mai sauƙi don lura da maki bisa ga gwaji na asibiti.
