Bangladesh ta samu sabbin mutane biyar da suka mutu sakamakon cutar COVID-19, wanda ya fi kowacce rana
Bangladesh ta tabbatar da cewa mutane biyar sun mutu a ranar saboda cutar COVID-19.
Wannan shi ne adadin mutuwar da aka yi a rana daya da cutar.
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka da Bincike (IEDCR) ta Bangladesh ta ruwaito cewa, har zuwa jiya, adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar sun kai 114 da suka yi aiki kuma 33 sun warke daga gidajen.
An samu mutuwar mutane 17.
Daraktan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka da Bincike, Dr. Mirjadine Sabrina Flora, a wani taron manema labarai na kan layi, ta ruwaito cewa, mutuwar ta shafi maza hudu da mace guda.
Kamar yadda Dr. Mergady ya ambata, akwai mutane biyu da suka wuce shekara 60, da kuma mutane biyu da suka kai shekaru 51 zuwa 60, da kuma mutum daya da ke tsakanin shekaru 41 zuwa 50.
