Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta bayyana cewa COVID-19 na da ciwo
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya WHO ta sanar a ranar Laraba cewa ci gaba da barkewar cutar COVID-19 - cuta da cutar coronavirus da ke tattare da cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani da ake kira SARS-CoV-2 - ta kai matakin annoba.
Ko da yake kalmar "zazzabi" tana nufin yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda yanayin da ke faruwa yake da tsanani ba, WHO ta yi gargaɗi cewa ya kamata gwamnatoci su ɗauki matakan da suka dace:
"Dukkanin kasashe za su iya canja yanayin annobar.
Babban darektan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, Tedros Adhanom Gibresos, ya ce: "Idan ƙasashe sun gano, sun yi bincike, sun warkar da mutane, sun ware su, sun biye musu, kuma sun tattara su don fuskantar".
"Dukanmu muna matukar damuwa game da yadda ake yaduwa da kuma yadda ake nuna hadarin da ake yi da kuma yadda ake nuna hadarin".
Kamar yadda Dokta Tom Freuden, tsohon darektan cibiyoyin hana cututtuka a Amirka ya ce, wannan annoba "ba ta taɓa faruwa ba".
A wata sanarwa da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu, ya ce, "Ba a bi hanyar wani kwayar cutar numfashi ba tun daga farkon bayyanar zuwa ci gaba da yaduwar duniya, banda mura".
Gibresus ya yi irin wannan bayanin: "Ba mu taɓa fuskantar annoba da ta faru da wani kwayar cutar korona ba".
Ya ci gaba da cewa: "Ba mu taɓa ganin wata annoba da za a iya sarrafawa a lokaci guda ba".
An bayyana sabon yanayin a matsayin annoba bayan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya a watan Janairu ta bayyana cewa cutar ta haifar da dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya ta duniya.
Darakta Anthony Fauci, darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Ƙasa a Amirka, ya ce game da annobar: "Abin da ya fi muhimmanci shi ne cewa abubuwa za su ƙara muni".
Hukumar ta Associated Press ta ruwaito cewa, aƙalla mutane 126,000 ne suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a duniya tun ranar Alhamis, kuma fiye da 4,600 sun mutu.
