An gano barkewar cutar a Wuhan, China, a watan Disambar 2019, kuma an ayyana ta a matsayin dokar ta baci ta lafiyar jama'a ta kasa da kasa a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma an bayyana ta a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, an samu kimanin mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da COVID-19 a kasashe da yankuna 210 kuma hakan ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 97,000.
