A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Red Cross ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta aika da tallafin dala miliyan 2.26 zuwa kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da kyautar fuska miliyan ɗaya ga Wuhan, Turkiyya ta aika da kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika da fiye da tan 13 na kayayyakin kiwon lafiya zuwa Wuhan, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da kyautar safofin hannu miliyan 18 ga China, Jamus ta ba da kayan kiwon lafiya da dama ciki har da riguna masu kariya 10,000, Amurka ta ba da tan 17.8 na kayan kiwon lafiya ga China, kuma ta yi alkawarin samar da ƙarin tallafi na kuɗi na dala miliyan 100 ga ƙasashe da ke fama da cutar. Bayan da yanayin ya daidaita a China, jihar ta aika da agaji ga ƙasashe daban-daban da suka lalace saboda annoba.
A watan Maris, kasar Sin da Cuba da kuma Rasha sun aika da kayan aikin likita da kuma masana don taimakawa Italiya wajen magance annobar korona.
Wani dan kasuwa mai suna Jack Ma ya aika wa Addis Ababa, Habasha, da tarin gwaje-gwaje miliyan 1.1, da masks miliyan shida, da kuma riguna 60,000 da kungiyar tarayyar Afirka ta yi wa rarrabawa.
Daga baya, sai aka tura masa wasu gwaje-gwaje 5,000 da kuma fuska 100,000 da kuma na'urori biyar na numfashi.
Ƙari ga haka, Ma ta ba da kayan aikin likita ga Kanada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkiyya, Georgia, da Jamhuriyar Czech sun nuna damuwarsu game da masks da kuma gwajin gwaji da aka yi a China.
Alal misali, Spain ta janye nau'ikan gwajin cutar korona 58,000 da aka yi a kasar Sin da suka kai kashi 30% kawai, kuma a lokacin, Netherlands ta dawo da masks 600,000 da aka yi a kasar Sin da suka lalace.
Belgium ta mayar da masks 100,000 da aka yi zaton sun fito ne daga kasar Sin amma a gaskiya sun fito ne daga Colombia.
A gefe guda kuma, sassan Latin Amurka da Afirka sun yi maraba da taimakon da kasar Sin ke bayarwa. A ranar 2 ga Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya kaddamar da ayyukan gaggawa na tallafawa kasashe masu tasowa.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta yaba wa kokarin da gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi na sarrafa cutar da kuma hana ta yaduwa.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta lura da bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS tsakanin shekara ta 2002 da 2004, inda hukumomin kasar Sin suka zargi ta da yin duhu wanda ya hana rigakafi da kuma hanawa, da kuma rikicin da ke faruwa a yanzu, inda gwamnatin tsakiya ta ba da "sabuntawa na yau da kullum don kauce wa firgita kafin sabuwar shekara ta wata".
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, a mayar da martani ga shawarar da hukumomin tsakiya suka yanke na aiwatar da haramcin sufuri a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gudun Gallaya ya lura cewa yayin da wannan "ba shakka ba ne shawarar da WHO ta bayar", amma "mai matukar muhimmanci ne ga nuna cewa an dage da cutar a inda take da matukar damuwa", ya bayyana ta a matsayin "ba a taɓa gani ba a tarihin lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan an tabbatar da cewa an koma daga kasar Sin zuwa waje, da kuma karuwar adadin shari'o'in a wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta bayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya ta kasa da kasa (BHIC), lamarin na shida daga cikin dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya da kasashe ke neman mafaka ga al'umma tun lokacin da suka yi rashin lafiya a cikin shekarar 2009.
Babban daraktan WHO ya ce, an dauki barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya na duniya saboda "hadarin yaduwar duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu karamin da matsakaicin kudin shiga waɗanda ba su da tsarin kiwon lafiya mai ƙarfi.
A cikin martani ga aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya ce "babu wani dalili da za a yi amfani da shi don yin amfani da shi ba tare da izini ba" da kuma "Kungiyar Lafiya ta Duniya ba ta ba da shawarar rage kasuwanci da sufuri".
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya da su ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 a cikin asusun dabarun da aka shirya a ƙasashen da ke da ƙananan kuɗin shiga, suna nuna gaggawa don tallafa wa waɗancan ƙasashen da "ba su da tsarin gano mutanen da ke da cutar, ko da sun bayyana".
Tedros ya kuma yi sharhi cewa "ƙarfinmu yana auna shi ne da ƙarfin mafi rauni a cikinmu" kuma ya bukaci al'ummar duniya su " zuba jari a yau ko kuma su biya babban farashi daga baya". A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta sanar da cutar, a wani taron manema labarai, da sunan COVID-19.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya ruwaito cewa Sakataren Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya Antonio Guterres ya amince da gabatar da "dukan damar tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a cikin amsawa".
A sakamakon haka, an kafa tawagar gudanar da rikicin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda ya ba da damar daidaita cikakken amsa na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, kuma WHO za ta ba shi damar "daidaita mayar da hankali kan amsawar lafiya yayin da za a iya amfani da ƙwarewar sauran hukumomi don sanin tasirin zamantakewa, tattalin arziki, da ci gaban da ya fi girma na annobar".
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, an shirya wata ƙungiya ta haɗin gwiwa da WHO ta jagoranci tare da China don gabatar da masana na duniya da masana na WHO a kan ƙasa a China don taimakawa gudanar da gida da kimanta "ciwo da kuma yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar" ta hanyar shirya bita da taro tare da manyan cibiyoyin ƙasa, da yin ziyara a filin don kimanta " tasirin ayyukan amsawa a larduna da birane, gami da birane da karkara. A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta sanar da cewa "duniya tana buƙatar yin ƙarin shiri don yiwuwar cutar coronavirus", ta ce tun da farko saboda an bayyana ta a matsayin mai yunwa, amma dole ne a nuna cewa "tafiyar cutar tana cikin wani mataki".
A cikin martani ga yaduwar cutar a Iran, WHO ta aika da wata ƙungiya ta hadin gwiwa don tantance halin da ake ciki. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce kimantawar barazanar cutar coronavirus a duniya za ta tashi daga "babba" zuwa "mafi girma", wanda shine mafi girman matakin gargadi da kimanta haɗari.
Mike Ryan, darektan shirin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya na WHO, ya yi gargadin a cikin wata sanarwa cewa, "Wannan gwaji ne na gaske ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: don haka dole ne mu kasance a shirye.
Wannan cutar na iya zuwa, kuma dole ne ku kasance a shirye don ta, kuma ya bukaci a dauki matakan da za su taimaka wa duniya ta kauce wa "abin da ya fi muni".
Ryan ya kuma ce bayanan da ake samu a yanzu ba sa sa sabawa jami'an lafiya na duniya su bayyana cutar a matsayin annoba ta duniya, yana mai cewa irin wannan sanarwar tana nufin "mu a zahiri mun yarda cewa kowane mutum a duniya zai kamu da cutar".
A ranar 11 ga Maris, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana barkewar cutar korona a matsayin annoba.
Darakta janar ya ce WHO "ta damu ƙwarai da mummunan matakan yaduwar, tsanani, da kuma matakan rashin ƙarfi". WHO ta fuskanci mummunan zargi game da abin da aka gani a matsayin rashin isasshen maganin cutar, ciki har da jinkirin bayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya ta jama'a, da kuma rarraba cutar a matsayin annoba.
A sakamakon haka, an yi kira ga babban darektan WHO, Tedros Adhanum, ya yi murabus, kuma mutane 733,000 ne suka yi sa hannu a kan wannan takardar tun daga ranar 6 ga Afrilu.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, da dama daga cikin masana kare hakkin bil adama na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sun tabbatar da girmama hakkin kowa a lokacin annobar COVID-19.
Kungiyar ta ce kowa yana da hakkin yin amfani da taimakon da zai ceci rayuka kuma gwamnati ce take da wannan hakkin.
Kungiyar ta jaddada cewa rashin albarkatu ko inshorar lafiya bai kamata ya zama dalilin nuna bambanci ga wani rukuni ba.
Masana sun tabbatar da cewa kowa yana da hakkin samun lafiya, ciki har da nakasassu, 'yan tsiraru, tsofaffi, marasa gida, marasa gida, waɗanda ke rayuwa cikin mummunan yanayi, fursunoni, da 'yan gudun hijira da sauran ɓangarorin da ba a bayyana ba da ke bukatar tallafin gwamnati.
Kungiyoyin gwamnati na duniya suna magance tasirin tattalin arziki da zamantakewar al'umma na rikicin COVID-19.
