An gudanar da nazarin ci gaban asibiti na alluran rigakafi da kuma abubuwan da ke tattare da COVID-19 tun daga watan Afrilu 2020. Ana yin nazarin magungunan antiviral da yawa da ke akwai don maganin COVID-19, ciki har da Remediciver, Chlorokine, Hydroxychloroquine, Lupinavir/Retonavir, Lupinavir/Tonavir da aka haɗa tare da Interferon Beta.
Akwai hujjoji na farko na yadda Remdesivir ke aiki, tun daga Maris 2020.
An lura da ci gaba a cikin asibiti a cikin marasa lafiya da aka yi musu magani da Remdesivir don amfani da alherin.
Ana gudanar da gwaji na asibiti na uku a Amurka, China da Italiya. An yi nazarin chloroquine, wanda a baya aka yi amfani da shi don maganin zazzabin cizon sauro a kasar Sin a watan Fabrairun 2020, kuma yana da sakamako na farko.
