A ranar 28 ga Maris, 2020, Hukumar Abinci da Magunguna ta ba da izinin gaggawa don amfani da hydroxychloroquine da chlorokin a cewar likitoci masu kula da waɗanda ke fama da COVID-19. Shafin 7 na jagororin kasar Sin ya hada da interferon, ribavirin ko omefenovir don amfani da maganin COVID-19.
Bayanai na farko sun nuna cewa ana bukatar karin rigakafin ribavirin don hana SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
An ba da shawarar yin ƙarin bincike game da tasirin nitasoxaneid a cikin kwayoyin halitta bayan an tabbatar da hana shi don ƙananan ƙwayar SARS-CoV-2. Nazarin ya nuna cewa farkon tsari na furotin Spike ta hanyar membrane-transfer serine protease 2 (TMPRS2) yana da mahimmanci don shigar da SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar hulɗa da mai karɓar ACE2.
Nazarin chloroquine da hydroxychloroquine tare da azithromycin ko kuma ba tare da shi ba sun ƙunshi manyan rashi da suka hana al'ummar likitanci karɓar waɗannan hanyoyin magani ba tare da ƙarin bincike ba. Oseltamivir ba ya hana SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje kuma ba shi da sanannen aiki a cikin maganin COVID-19.
